data.title: MetroPlan Orlando
data.text:
We're Planning an End to Traffic Deaths with Vision Zero Central Florida

The ultimate goal? Achieve zero traffic fatalities and serious injuries on Central Florida's roads. See how MetroPlan Orlando is working with partners throughout the region to produce comprehensive Vision Zero Safety Action Plans that will save lives. And find out how you can help.

Learn More

Welcome to Metroplan Orlando

MetroPlan Orlando is the metropolitan planning organization for Orange, Osceola, and Seminole counties. We help the region create a vision for transportation 25 years into the future, with an emphasis on safety for all Central Floridians. We hope you’ll browse our website, starting with our Vision Zero Central Florida – Counting Down to Zero Traffic Deaths video, and take advantage of the wealth of transportation information we offer.
